org.apache.openjpa.kernel

Class DetachedStateManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.openjpa.kernel.DetachedStateManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, FieldConsumer, FieldManager, FieldSupplier, StateManager, OpenJPAStateManager

    public class DetachedStateManager
extends Object
implements OpenJPAStateManager, Serializable
    Internal state manager for detached instances. Does not fully implement OpenJPAStateManager contract to allow for serialization.
    Author:
    Steve Kim
